episodes.title: Cults Part 2: The 7M Tik Tok Cult
episodes.description:
This is part 2 of our episode on Cults. In Cults Part 2: The 7M Tik Tok Cult we will talk about the current situation with 7M. Is it a church? A talent agency? A terrible place to work? We’re not sure but many are convinced this is one of the latest cults to spring up in the United States. 




Warning: some language or themes may not be suitable for all ages.
